Author: maxxymoo0329
Text: Same here all three.. I have the worst skin because of my picking... My mum tells me to stop but I can't...but thank you for bringing me back to the reality that I still am self harming.

Author: virgotaurus
Text: Binge eating can be a form of self-harm. I think it helps to remember that self-harm can look like things other than cutting or burning or whatever. For me, I binge, pick my skin, and pull my hair.
